weaponState 
Game: ArmA 2: Operation Arrowhead (1.60) 
Description: Returns the current weapon state as an array of strings in the following 
 format [WeaponName, MuzzleName, ModeName, MagazineName, AmmoCount 
] (AmmoCount is Number).  
Syntax:  
 weaponState unitName 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object 
Return Value: 
 Array: ["m16a4","m16a4","Single","30Rnd_556x45_Stanag",29]